  "title": "Kitchen & Service Crew / 5day (Japanese Cuisine)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Join Our Reputable Japanese Food &amp; Beverage Group</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Kitchen Crew – What You’ll Do:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prepare and cook menu items in accordance with operational requirements.</li>\n  <li>Maintain a high level of food hygiene, safety, and cleanliness in the kitchen.</li>\n  <li>Assist in dishwashing and cleaning tasks as needed.</li>\n  <li>Support kitchen operations with additional duties as directed by management.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Service Crew – What You’ll Do:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Greet customers with warmth and provide excellent service throughout their visit.</li>\n  <li>Accurately take and process customer orders for food and beverages.</li>\n  <li>Serve food and drinks efficiently and courteously.</li>\n  <li>Maintain the cleanliness and tidiness of dining and service areas.</li>\n  <li>Assist with any additional tasks as required by the management team.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Why Join Us</strong></p>\n<p>** No prior experience necessary – just bring your enthusiasm and willingness to learn.</p>\n<p><strong>Salary &amp; Bonus:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Basic salary of <strong>$1,750</strong> plus a <strong>$1,000 joining bonus</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Attractive Benefits:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>AWS (Annual Wage Supplement) and performance-based bonus</li>\n  <li>Annual leave with public holiday entitlement</li>\n  <li>Birthday vouchers to celebrate your special day</li>\n  <li>Medical and dental insurance for your health and well-being</li>\n  <li>Complimentary staff meals during working hours</li>\n  <li>Overtime pay entitlement</li>\n  <li>Clear career progression opportunities within the company</li>\n  <li>Uniform provided with comprehensive training to ensure your success</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Work Schedule:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>5-day work week, 44 hours total (schedule based on outlet operations)</li>\n  <li>Minimum of 30 hours of overtime per month</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p><br></p>",
